&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;in EQ terms, this would be like a rune, that only worked at half health, and absorbed roughly 3k damage it would cost a emerald or so. &lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
